    About Kati Spaniak


    The Spaniak Team has an understanding of Northbrook unlike any other real estate agent or team. Team Leader, Kati Spaniak grew up in Northbrook and is still residing in town. Her team sells more real estate than anyone in District 28. Her children have attended both public and private schools in Northbrook, and Kati was a village trustee. No one understands the ins and outs of Northbrook, the schools and the village like Kati and her team.
